Package org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.helperClasses.routing

Class routeNode

java.lang.Object
org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.helperClasses.routing.routeNode
public class routeNode extends Object
This class represents each point of a route where the robot should move, and what it should do while moving there/on arrival.
